CustomField.description: When you update the json there is a test deserialization. At the sametime a checksum will be created to indicate this has been done.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: When you update the json there is a test deserialization. At the sametime a checksum will be created to indicate this has been done. If the deserialization fails the job will be marked inactive and the error message will be shown instead.
CustomField.label: JSON Checksum
